- Here. I'm here.

1081
00:46:05,020 --> 00:46:07,260
Princess! Princess!

1082
00:46:07,260 --> 00:46:08,140
What's up?

1083
00:46:08,140 --> 00:46:09,580
Breathe before you speak.

1084
00:46:11,060 --> 00:46:11,900
Xu Qi'an...

1085
00:46:12,140 --> 00:46:13,500
